==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Contra
<hw>Con"tra</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>. <def>A Latin adverb and preposition,
signifying <xex>against</xex>, <xex>contrary</xex>, <xex>in
opposition</xex>, etc., entering as a prefix into the composition of
many English words. Cf. <er>Counter</er>, <pos>adv. &
pref.</pos></def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Contraband</ent>⟦br⟧
